http: Displays all HTTP traffic
dns: Displays all DNS queries and responses
arp: Displays all ARP packets
tcp: Shows all TCP traffic
udp: Shows all UDP traffic
icmp: Displays ping and ICMP traffic
ip.addr == "specifc ip address": Shows traffic to/from a specific IP address
tcp.port == 80: Shows traffic using HTTP port 80
tcp.port == 443: Shows HTTPS traffic
dns.flags.response == 0: Displays only DNS requests
dns.flags.response == 1: Displays only DNS responses
http.request.method == "GET": Shows HTTP GET requests only
arp.opcode == 1: Shows ARP Requests
arp.opcode == 2: Shows ARP Replies
